posting_body: ['Property Address', '608 Lincoln Ave - 207 | St. Paul, MN 55102', 'Available: 10/01/2022', 'Offered By', 'At Home Apartments', 'Description', 'Pleasant Corner Apartment at The Oakviews', 'This corner, one-bedroom apartment has a unique Pullman rail-car inspired layout.', 'Enjoy plenty of sunlight with south and west-facing windows.', 'Hardwood floors, a pedestal sink, and original built-in cabinetry give this apartment a cozy, historic feel.', 'Additional updated kitchen cabinets give the apartment a modern touch.', 'Built in 1919, the Oakview Apartments offer charming studio and one-bedroom apartments.', 'Have the best of both worlds by being located along a quiet street among stately Victorian homes and just one block from bustling Grand Avenue.', 'Enjoy the historic charm of this beautiful, brownstone building.', 'Residents have included access to the clubhouse and fitness center just one mile away!', 'Oakview residents have access to unlimited convenient, coinless on-site laundry for a flat monthly fee.', 'Call us at', 'show contact info', 'or visit us at <URL> for more information and tour options.', 'Photos are a representation of the property and may not be of the exact apartment.', '**$150 Administration Fee added to lease.', 'Final price subject to change pending walk-through inspection.', 'Pet fees/restrictions may apply.', 'Please inquire about your specific pet.', '**', 'Amenities', 'Hardwood Floors', 'Walk-in Closet', 'Fitness Center and Clubhouse One Mile Away', 'Heat/Water/Trash Paid', 'Coinless Laundry On-Site', '*24 hour Emergency Maintenance', 'Bike Storage', 'Online Rent Payment Portal', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 600', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,004.00', 'Available: 10/01/2022', 'Application Fee: $55.00', 'Security Deposit: $600.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
